<p>Perhaps thatâ€™s not what you mean when you say you lack inspiration to write. Maybe you mean you arenâ€™t inspired to write about anything interesting. Okay, but donâ€™t let that stop you from writing. â€œNot having inspirationâ€ is no excuse to stop. You are perfectly capable of describing your bedroom or the route you take to work. So do so.</p>

